      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a great project car or a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a few small dings around the door panels. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, but it will likely require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in top shape. It\u2019s an honest car at an honest price.",
