      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, maintained to a standard that rivals its original showroom debut. This vehicle exhibits flawless aesthetic and mechanical integrity, representing a rare find for the most discerning buyer. Every surface and component has been preserved with exacting care, ensuring a driving experience of peerless refinement. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
