      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. You won't find a single scratch or dent on it! It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
