    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L straight-six power plant. This specimen is mechanically flawless, having undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and proactive rod bearing replacement using ARP hardware. The VANOS system has been precision-serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and throttle response across the 8,000 RPM range. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tight, notched engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains silent and effective. The exterior finish maintains exceptional depth with zero clear coat failure, while the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster compression or wear. Every bushing is factory-spec and the suspension geometry is dialed for the purist. This is a turn-key, investment-quality example of the ultimate driving machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
